00:00:11.484 --> 00:00:16.484
Yesterday, you had asked me

00:00:17.026 --> 00:00:19.026
for the status of a Guru.

00:00:21.645 --> 00:00:24.948
It's a state,

00:00:26.338 --> 00:00:29.564
it is not a status because status

00:00:30.615 --> 00:00:33.610
is external, can be bestowed upon anyone,

00:00:35.127 --> 00:00:40.335
and anybody can say that this is your status.

00:00:43.038 --> 00:00:45.742
For something external merit, or something,

00:00:46.793 --> 00:00:48.396
you can give a status to a person. 

00:00:49.277 --> 00:00:50.391
It is a state.

00:00:51.357 --> 00:00:53.978
State means the innate being,

00:00:55.770 --> 00:00:58.514
evolved to that level

00:01:00.137 --> 00:01:04.306
that you become the master.

00:01:07.836 --> 00:01:08.713
Of course

00:01:12.688 --> 00:01:16.776
you have to be your own master to begin with, no doubt about it.

00:01:18.335 --> 00:01:20.760
If you are not even your own master

00:01:22.044 --> 00:01:23.765
then how you can

00:01:26.234 --> 00:01:27.481
achieve that state.

00:01:30.417 --> 00:01:32.417
Now as I say it is innate.

00:01:34.082 --> 00:01:36.253
Then one starts thinking

00:01:36.969 --> 00:01:39.515
if it is innate in a Sahaj way

00:01:40.520 --> 00:01:41.880
how do we achieve it.

00:01:51.498 --> 00:01:53.498
There are certain faculties,

00:01:54.989 --> 00:01:57.406
which we have to develop to begin with.

00:02:01.672 --> 00:02:03.672
The first faculty is

00:02:07.596 --> 00:02:09.596
if you can become thoughtless.

00:02:12.997 --> 00:02:14.468
In meditation

00:02:15.292 --> 00:02:17.292
you can become thoughtless

00:02:17.792 --> 00:02:18.623
for a short time.

00:02:20.618 --> 00:02:22.618
Gradually this short time

00:02:24.001 --> 00:02:25.619
should go on increasing,

00:02:26.119 --> 00:02:28.119
that you are without any thought.

00:02:32.114 --> 00:02:34.773
This happens also as we can say is a state,

00:02:38.354 --> 00:02:41.640
but how do we achieve that, again,

00:02:42.338 --> 00:02:44.721
because human beings cannot understand

00:02:45.221 --> 00:02:47.550
that anything can happen spontaneously

00:02:47.582 --> 00:02:50.589
it has to be done somehow, something has to be done.

00:02:52.260 --> 00:02:55.092
For that in Sahaj

00:02:56.547 --> 00:02:59.083
we have something very very simple,

00:03:03.475 --> 00:03:08.261
that you have got a mantra as Nirvichara.

00:03:11.356 --> 00:03:13.627
So now you watch anything 

00:03:14.902 --> 00:03:15.997
saying the mantra

00:03:17.578 --> 00:03:19.632
Om twameva sakshat Nirvichara

00:03:21.862 --> 00:03:24.635
Then you'll start seeing that,

00:03:24.937 --> 00:03:25.901
witnessing that

00:03:27.842 --> 00:03:29.842
without thinking.

00:03:33.189 --> 00:03:34.603
Just see, witness.

00:03:38.815 --> 00:03:40.815
Just seeing itself

00:03:42.847 --> 00:03:46.518
creates that state within us the first state, is very important

00:03:47.468 --> 00:03:49.936
that you become the witness, the 'Sakshi'.

00:03:56.634 --> 00:03:59.900
As soon as you become the Sakshi,

00:04:04.310 --> 00:04:06.310
the whole thing whatever you are seeing

00:04:11.278 --> 00:04:14.389
gives you a complete idea,

00:04:15.646 --> 00:04:19.052
subtle as well as gross of that thing.

00:04:20.111 --> 00:04:23.633
You see it and you know it

00:04:26.349 --> 00:04:27.900
and as a Sahaja yogi

00:04:28.400 --> 00:04:30.400
it becomes your knowledge.

00:04:31.693 --> 00:04:33.693
We can say in the modern terminology

00:04:35.761 --> 00:04:37.761
that you see something,

00:04:39.756 --> 00:04:42.176
it gets recorded in your mind

00:04:44.388 --> 00:04:46.388
and it manifests joy,

00:04:48.654 --> 00:04:50.654
it manifests knowledge,

00:04:53.064 --> 00:04:56.540
it manifests compassion, whatever may the situation,

00:04:58.986 --> 00:05:01.441
because now you have many dimensions

00:05:03.364 --> 00:05:04.411
which you have to develop,

00:05:05.902 --> 00:05:07.902
these dimensions are to be developed.

00:05:09.645 --> 00:05:11.645
Now supposing you go and meet someone

00:05:13.082 --> 00:05:14.195
with whom you have to deal.

00:05:17.975 --> 00:05:19.975
He's talking, talking, talking,

00:05:21.448 --> 00:05:23.448
just become thoughtless.

00:05:24.867 --> 00:05:28.131
So know what is the thing that will happen as soon as you become thoughtless.

00:05:28.631 --> 00:05:30.631
First his thoughts,

00:05:30.789 --> 00:05:32.789
his bombardment will not touch you

00:05:33.055 --> 00:05:35.365
because you are in a different realm altogether.

00:05:36.388 --> 00:05:38.388
But in that realm

00:05:42.185 --> 00:05:44.185
your power will manifest.

00:05:45.262 --> 00:05:47.262
It may cool him down,

00:05:48.050 --> 00:05:50.050
it will shut him down

00:05:51.307 --> 00:05:53.307
or maybe he may just

00:05:53.807 --> 00:05:56.454
feel tremendous love for you.

00:06:04.702 --> 00:06:07.855
So the word Guru means Gravity.

00:06:10.661 --> 00:06:12.661
That the Mother Earth has gravity.

00:06:14.566 --> 00:06:17.805
In the same a person who is a Guru

00:06:18.197 --> 00:06:20.654
has to have the gravity.

00:06:21.550 --> 00:06:23.550
But how do you develop this gravity.

00:06:25.257 --> 00:06:27.257
Some people just

00:06:27.307 --> 00:06:29.307
artificially become very grave

00:06:30.924 --> 00:06:32.136
and sometimes

00:06:32.726 --> 00:06:35.273
show that they are very serious or something like that.

00:06:38.169 --> 00:06:40.169
Gravity is within yourself.

00:06:43.011 --> 00:06:45.011
In the second state, we should say,

00:06:46.970 --> 00:06:50.827
of guru Pada is your gravity must manifest.

00:06:51.994 --> 00:06:53.994
As you become the witness

00:06:54.296 --> 00:06:56.825
your gravity starts expressing itself.

00:06:58.280 --> 00:07:01.786
It will not show as temper

00:07:01.890 --> 00:07:04.328
or seriousness or anything like that.

00:07:05.116 --> 00:07:08.652
But it will manifest in a way that

00:07:11.963 --> 00:07:15.234
the whole thing will become extremely dignified

00:07:16.220 --> 00:07:17.076
and majestic.

00:07:17.576 --> 00:07:19.576
It will just manifest by itself.

00:07:21.463 --> 00:07:25.645
So the state in which you rise,

00:07:27.028 --> 00:07:29.028
now becomes effective.

00:07:31.078 --> 00:07:33.078
Before this it was not.

00:07:34.209 --> 00:07:36.209
You had to all the time

00:07:38.096 --> 00:07:40.619
manipulate, say this, say that.

00:07:42.741 --> 00:07:44.741
But in your silence

00:07:45.421 --> 00:07:48.888
you can manifest your gravity,

00:07:50.595 --> 00:07:53.549
and this gravity is extremely...

00:07:55.403 --> 00:07:57.403
it acts like a magnet.

00:07:58.769 --> 00:08:00.769
As you know there is a magnet in the Mother Earth.

00:08:02.388 --> 00:08:06.359
That we call as the gravity by which people are attracted.

00:08:07.996 --> 00:08:10.426
We are resting on this Mother Earth

00:08:10.511 --> 00:08:11.985
because of her gravity.

00:08:14.022 --> 00:08:16.670
Everything is attracted to Mother Earth

00:08:16.827 --> 00:08:18.611
because of her gravity.

00:08:21.060 --> 00:08:23.988
So you get a magnetic temperament, magnetic

00:08:25.950 --> 00:08:26.807
character,

00:08:29.130 --> 00:08:30.437
magnetic personality.

00:08:32.092 --> 00:08:34.092
And this magnetic personality

00:08:35.693 --> 00:08:36.682
that you develop,

00:08:38.193 --> 00:08:43.124
immediately shows that it is manifesting its power,

00:08:43.985 --> 00:08:45.104
try to understand.

00:08:46.940 --> 00:08:49.228
Like the light now is coming on me

00:08:49.890 --> 00:08:51.353
it is just giving light,

00:08:51.979 --> 00:08:53.979
but it is not manifesting anything.

00:08:56.410 --> 00:08:59.150
We can see the sun's rays, is the best example.

00:09:00.210 --> 00:09:04.471
Sun's rays when they fall onto the leaves,

00:09:06.776 --> 00:09:08.776
the rays, which look simple,

00:09:09.276 --> 00:09:14.032
manifest their power of making it into chlorophyll.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:18.393
In the same way when you are

00:09:19.074 --> 00:09:21.074
at that height

00:09:21.484 --> 00:09:23.952
or at that state then

00:09:24.452 --> 00:09:25.904
without saying anything,

00:09:27.144 --> 00:09:29.144
without doing anything, even a glance,

00:09:33.489 --> 00:09:38.319
you manifest but not only that, but you record everything.

00:09:42.104 --> 00:09:44.104
So many people must have noticed

00:09:45.922 --> 00:09:47.922
that I seldom forget things.

00:09:48.873 --> 00:09:50.873
Like once I was travelling

00:09:52.239 --> 00:09:56.629
and I saw some red stones near Sangamne,

00:09:57.977 --> 00:10:01.601
and when I said that why not we have some red stones for Pratishtan.

00:10:02.408 --> 00:10:05.274
They said "but there are no red stones in the whole of Maharastra."

00:10:05.305 --> 00:10:07.305
I said "there are". "Where?",

00:10:07.805 --> 00:10:11.941
I said "go on the way you'll find them near Sangamne.",

00:10:12.712 --> 00:10:15.341
they said "we have travelled so much, we have never seen.",

00:10:15.949 --> 00:10:17.949
I said "I don't know what you are seeing you know,

00:10:19.063 --> 00:10:21.503
what you are watching, I have definitely seen."

00:10:22.003 --> 00:10:25.740
When they went there they saw mountains and mountains of these red stones

00:10:26.619 --> 00:10:28.619
and they never noticed it even.

00:10:33.650 --> 00:10:34.353
So now

00:10:36.658 --> 00:10:39.836
when you start witnessing something without thought

00:10:41.726 --> 00:10:44.033
there is no obstruction for absorbing

00:10:44.533 --> 00:10:46.533
the knowledge about that thing,

00:10:47.033 --> 00:10:48.109
because there is no thought.

00:10:50.540 --> 00:10:52.540
It's complete absorption takes place.

00:10:54.394 --> 00:10:56.394
And then it manifests.

00:11:00.739 --> 00:11:02.739
This is how

00:11:05.568 --> 00:11:07.930
the divine power works within us.

00:11:15.759 --> 00:11:18.120
So with our gravity

00:11:20.642 --> 00:11:25.059
what we do is to touch that depth within us,

00:11:25.559 --> 00:11:28.909
which can carry the divine power and manifest.

00:11:30.420 --> 00:11:33.163
Unless and until we touch that depth within us

00:11:34.331 --> 00:11:36.331
Sahaja yoga is like

00:11:38.383 --> 00:11:39.449
Hare Rama Hare Krishna.

00:11:43.433 --> 00:11:45.433
Nothing better than that

00:11:45.933 --> 00:11:47.933
and that's why I find so many Sahaja yogis

00:11:48.902 --> 00:11:54.757
sometimes really go off their rails suddenly.

00:11:56.051 --> 00:11:58.051
Because they have no gravity

00:11:59.291 --> 00:12:01.783
to go down into their own being

00:12:02.554 --> 00:12:05.761
and to feel the beauty and the glory of their own being

00:12:06.784 --> 00:12:08.784
and to use that gravity

00:12:10.764 --> 00:12:13.529
for manifesting divine power.

00:12:18.569 --> 00:12:19.778
We could say that

00:12:21.214 --> 00:12:24.622
supposing there is a vehicle, which is very weak,

00:12:27.540 --> 00:12:29.540
which is not yet properly fixed,

00:12:31.491 --> 00:12:36.157
can not be used for something substantial.

00:12:38.841 --> 00:12:44.052
And the most substantial thing in your lives is this divine power,

00:12:44.911 --> 00:12:48.277
which looks very light;

00:12:49.557 --> 00:12:51.557
you never feel the weight of this divine power.

00:12:53.523 --> 00:12:56.309
You'll never feel the pressure of this divine power

00:13:00.272 --> 00:13:02.602
but if you are not clean,

00:13:04.678 --> 00:13:06.834
if your channel is not clean

00:13:07.771 --> 00:13:10.827
then this divine power cannot flow properly,

00:13:11.920 --> 00:13:12.616
it cannot manifest.

00:13:13.849 --> 00:13:17.963
So when we say that we are the instruments of God Almighty

00:13:18.463 --> 00:13:20.212
then like this instrument we are,

00:13:20.712 --> 00:13:22.307
now we are connected to the mains.

00:13:22.604 --> 00:13:25.641
If this instrument is not all right

00:13:25.954 --> 00:13:28.452
than it cannot manifest

00:13:28.952 --> 00:13:30.449
whatever it is supposed to do.

00:13:32.337 --> 00:13:34.337
But we are much above

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:38.677
all these ordinary instruments,

00:13:39.427 --> 00:13:40.900
even the most complicated,

00:13:42.539 --> 00:13:47.252
even the most advanced and developed by science.

00:13:48.329 --> 00:13:50.329
Because we reach a state where

00:13:51.453 --> 00:13:54.497
we ourselves become the science.

00:13:55.824 --> 00:13:58.990
Science of truth, an absolute truth.

00:14:00.832 --> 00:14:06.597
So what is needed for a Guru is self esteem.

00:14:08.688 --> 00:14:12.912
This is a very important point people don't realise, the self-esteem.

00:14:16.267 --> 00:14:18.267
To achieve the self-esteem

00:14:18.767 --> 00:14:20.325
we have to introspect

00:14:21.184 --> 00:14:23.433
and know that today

00:14:23.574 --> 00:14:26.477
I am not what I was before.

00:14:27.975 --> 00:14:29.099
I am a realised soul,

00:14:30.847 --> 00:14:34.317
I have got powers. Of course I have powers.

00:14:35.020 --> 00:14:37.770
Powers of love, powers of compassion,

00:14:38.972 --> 00:14:40.980
powers of grasping things,

00:14:43.945 --> 00:14:45.464
powers of creativity,

00:14:48.491 --> 00:14:52.514
powers of giving realisations to others.

00:14:53.919 --> 00:14:55.296
Nobody had these powers

00:14:57.060 --> 00:15:00.208
but somehow or other in Sahaja Yoga you are not self conscious,

00:15:01.800 --> 00:15:03.533
and we should not be self conscious

00:15:03.581 --> 00:15:05.581
because that can give you ego

00:15:06.081 --> 00:15:08.747
but we should have self esteem.

00:15:10.261 --> 00:15:11.026
I am a Guru,

00:15:12.899 --> 00:15:16.714
I am a Guru, I am not an ordinary person.

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:19.093
I am not on the street,

00:15:20.435 --> 00:15:22.435
I am something special

00:15:23.325 --> 00:15:26.905
and on the shores of truth,

00:15:28.169 --> 00:15:30.169
I have to salvage the people

00:15:30.903 --> 00:15:33.628
who are blind, who are mad.

00:15:34.970 --> 00:15:35.808
All kinds of things.

00:15:37.540 --> 00:15:41.173
In the most chaotic conditions this world is today.

00:15:43.108 --> 00:15:46.641
So at that time a kind of a silence

00:15:49.372 --> 00:15:50.405
will come within you.

00:15:51.857 --> 00:15:53.841
When there will be any such crisis,

00:15:53.920 --> 00:15:56.836
immediately you will become extremely silent.

00:15:57.336 --> 00:15:59.336
But this is again a state I am telling you.

00:16:00.990 --> 00:16:02.990
So now, if there is

00:16:03.709 --> 00:16:06.859
something that makes you upset

00:16:09.169 --> 00:16:10.588
or makes you unhappy,

00:16:13.116 --> 00:16:16.080
try to reach that point that axis

00:16:16.908 --> 00:16:18.908
which is just silence,

00:16:21.498 --> 00:16:24.755
and this silence will make you really powerful

00:16:25.255 --> 00:16:28.077
because this silence is not only yours.

00:16:29.903 --> 00:16:33.915
When you are in that silence you are in the silence of the cosmos,

00:16:35.959 --> 00:16:37.385
silence of the cosmos.

00:16:38.462 --> 00:16:40.462
And the silence of the cosmos

00:16:43.708 --> 00:16:44.553
works for you.

00:16:46.379 --> 00:16:47.582
You are in connection

00:16:52.778 --> 00:16:53.549
with that

00:16:54.579 --> 00:16:58.494
cosmic power we can call it but it's more than that it is divine power I should say.

00:17:00.195 --> 00:17:02.858
Divine power, which is working all the cosmos.

00:17:07.648 --> 00:17:08.438
So if you

00:17:12.604 --> 00:17:13.010
just

00:17:14.789 --> 00:17:16.631
become silent within yourself,

00:17:17.505 --> 00:17:20.896
know that you are sitting in the kingdom of God.

00:17:26.373 --> 00:17:27.224
It's like this,

00:17:29.752 --> 00:17:32.722
when say you

00:17:33.674 --> 00:17:37.503
get the great honour

00:17:40.047 --> 00:17:42.505
of becoming a King

00:17:44.939 --> 00:17:47.460
then you walk up to a throne

00:17:48.880 --> 00:17:49.974
and you sit down

00:17:51.644 --> 00:17:52.621
and look around

00:17:54.603 --> 00:17:57.325
and you feel the silence

00:18:00.243 --> 00:18:05.263
of the state that now you are the King.

00:18:07.994 --> 00:18:08.951
This silence

00:18:10.465 --> 00:18:13.073
is the sign that you are definitely,

00:18:13.901 --> 00:18:17.941
definitely you are now

00:18:19.268 --> 00:18:23.748
in contact with the divine.

00:18:25.340 --> 00:18:28.798
You are silent because the divine is going to look after everything.

00:18:32.481 --> 00:18:34.901
You don't have to do anything, just keep silent.

00:18:36.680 --> 00:18:39.044
But not forcibly, it's again a state.

00:18:41.962 --> 00:18:45.425
See if any turmoil takes place, any problem takes place

00:18:46.767 --> 00:18:49.763
suddenly your attention will jump on to that silence

00:18:52.322 --> 00:18:54.834
and once you jump onto that silence

00:18:56.254 --> 00:19:00.031
you being in contact with this whole all pervading power.

00:19:00.656 --> 00:19:02.656
And when I talk about all pervading power

00:19:03.234 --> 00:19:05.234
we still don't understand what it is.

00:19:06.951 --> 00:19:10.481
What it means this all pervading power of love.

00:19:10.529 --> 00:19:13.693
Is it some sort of an energy floating around

00:19:14.583 --> 00:19:19.521
or is it some sort of a river

00:19:21.144 --> 00:19:24.141
or some sort of a ether.

00:19:29.181 --> 00:19:29.814
It is

00:19:34.089 --> 00:19:38.275
the complete, the totality of reality.

00:19:41.021 --> 00:19:43.664
Complete totality of reality,

00:19:45.084 --> 00:19:47.084
is this all pervading power.

00:19:48.738 --> 00:19:50.738
Other things are unreal.

00:19:55.419 --> 00:19:58.489
And the reality is so efficient.

00:20:10.814 --> 00:20:12.814
It is so efficient;

00:20:12.846 --> 00:20:14.846
it never fails, like this mike.

00:20:23.225 --> 00:20:25.225
It's such a tremendous;

00:20:27.987 --> 00:20:31.293
you can call the intertwined process,

00:20:34.055 --> 00:20:36.055
which we cannot even

00:20:38.692 --> 00:20:41.366
imagine with this human understanding.

00:20:45.251 --> 00:20:47.472
How it controls, how it works.

00:20:50.765 --> 00:20:52.765
Say for example

00:20:53.889 --> 00:20:54.847
you see the trees.

00:20:56.860 --> 00:21:01.085
Rosebush will give rose only it won't give apples.

00:21:02.958 --> 00:21:05.496
It will grow up to a certain height it won't grow

00:21:05.996 --> 00:21:07.463
like a coconut tree.

00:21:09.804 --> 00:21:12.457
All the characters of this

00:21:16.280 --> 00:21:21.103
nature is maintained, nourished, looked after,

00:21:21.899 --> 00:21:24.720
controlled absolutely at the right time,

00:21:26.718 --> 00:21:27.454
at the right

00:21:30.232 --> 00:21:34.305
seasons that's why in Sanskrit this is called as ritambara pragya.

00:21:34.805 --> 00:21:36.805
Roota means seasons

00:21:37.742 --> 00:21:41.203
and the one which looks after these seasons.

00:21:42.109 --> 00:21:44.266
That knowledge which is enlightened,

00:21:44.953 --> 00:21:46.953
a simple definition.

00:21:48.701 --> 00:21:51.844
But still it doesn't explain

00:21:53.186 --> 00:21:55.186
because it is so

00:21:57.605 --> 00:21:59.605
complicated for human brain

00:22:01.540 --> 00:22:03.540
that they cannot understand how it works.

