00:27:34.477 --> 00:27:38.552
silver or gold or diamonds or anything,

00:27:39.270 --> 00:27:40.156
it can never

00:27:41.904 --> 00:27:45.458
impress him and he can never go into imbalances.

00:27:56.940 --> 00:28:01.636
Food for example. Food is one of the weak points I think.

00:28:04.554 --> 00:28:08.127
A Guru who might eat quite a lot,

00:28:09.142 --> 00:28:11.142
may not eat at all,

00:28:14.232 --> 00:28:16.987
may like something to eat,

00:28:17.393 --> 00:28:19.393
something not to eat, whatever it is,

00:28:22.186 --> 00:28:26.905
but nothing can dominate this Guru.

00:28:29.495 --> 00:28:31.495
So the symptom

00:28:32.510 --> 00:28:34.897
is that you are in balance

00:28:36.629 --> 00:28:40.638
and you cannot be dominated by food

00:28:40.888 --> 00:28:45.722
or by power or by wealth or money or anything.

00:28:45.738 --> 00:28:47.093
Nothing can dominate you.

00:28:50.916 --> 00:28:52.916
You are above all these things.

00:28:55.553 --> 00:28:59.185
And once you know that you are above these things

00:29:02.883 --> 00:29:04.283
then you are not afraid.

00:29:06.015 --> 00:29:09.401
No more you are afraid. Fearlessness comes into you.

00:29:10.821 --> 00:29:12.821
Become absolutely fearless.

00:29:16.472 --> 00:29:22.041
Nothing can, nothing can put you into imbalance.

00:29:23.820 --> 00:29:25.820
Nothing can dominate you.

00:29:26.944 --> 00:29:28.944
Nothing can weaken you.

00:29:30.536 --> 00:29:32.536
Nothing can make you an addict.

00:29:35.438 --> 00:29:37.438
Nothing is tempting.

00:29:41.776 --> 00:29:45.049
There's nothing like temptation left anymore.

00:29:49.059 --> 00:29:52.469
When you reach that state, beyond temptation,

00:29:54.701 --> 00:29:57.376
beyond any greed, beyond any lust,

00:30:01.230 --> 00:30:01.890
then

00:30:06.384 --> 00:30:07.526
there is no

00:30:11.349 --> 00:30:16.116
problem, nothing; nothing can really bring you down.

00:30:20.891 --> 00:30:25.451
You may wear ordinary tulsi

00:30:25.951 --> 00:30:28.659
garland or you may wear

00:30:33.465 --> 00:30:35.465
pearls or diamonds or anything.

00:30:39.272 --> 00:30:41.272
That doesn't touch you,

00:30:42.755 --> 00:30:44.755
but you don't run away from anything

00:30:46.394 --> 00:30:50.359
because when you run away from something you become an ascetic artificially.

00:30:50.859 --> 00:30:53.713
Asceticism is within yourself, innate.

00:30:57.037 --> 00:31:00.467
So nothing can hamper you, nothing can matter.

00:31:06.614 --> 00:31:11.820
