00:43:39.770 --> 00:43:42.534
Kindness, sweetness, concern,

00:43:44.241 --> 00:43:46.510
that's what your Mother has given you,

00:43:48.499 --> 00:43:49.332
concern.

00:43:56.854 --> 00:43:58.854
The concern that flows

00:44:00.824 --> 00:44:02.824
about each and every person.

00:44:05.044 --> 00:44:07.044
You have to have concern.

00:44:08.670 --> 00:44:10.670
But these gurus "no you go,

00:44:11.577 --> 00:44:16.070
then die, kill yourself, eat grass."

00:44:20.011 --> 00:44:22.011
No not that way.

00:44:24.701 --> 00:44:28.696
So you also have to be a motherly guru.

00:44:32.418 --> 00:44:35.996
A sweet guru. Extremely sweet,

00:44:37.341 --> 00:44:38.717
kindly

00:44:42.720 --> 00:44:46.039
and understanding, forgiving.

00:44:49.229 --> 00:44:51.507
Because what is the purpose,

00:44:54.384 --> 00:44:56.384
what is the purpose?

00:44:57.009 --> 00:44:59.009
The purpose is to spread Sahaja Yoga.

00:45:00.260 --> 00:45:02.260
That's the main thing we miss out

00:45:02.760 --> 00:45:06.356
that the purpose of our realisation or of our birth

00:45:06.574 --> 00:45:09.116
is to give realisations to others,

00:45:09.272 --> 00:45:12.899
to spread Sahaja Yoga, to emancipate others,

00:45:12.961 --> 00:45:16.065
by that to emancipate the whole world, it's our responsibility.

00:45:18.192 --> 00:45:20.445
If you are responsible then how do you behave?

00:45:25.199 --> 00:45:28.918
So no more we have priesthood, no more.

00:45:29.418 --> 00:45:35.933
Nor that one person says so, that person says so, this has happened, nothing of the kind.

00:45:36.433 --> 00:45:39.232
What you have to say you say to that person.

00:45:41.077 --> 00:45:43.077
And you yourself will see

00:45:43.264 --> 00:45:47.376
how you are reflecting your personality on another person,

00:45:49.503 --> 00:45:51.108
how he reacts

00:45:53.203 --> 00:45:55.203
and how he behaves.

00:45:55.922 --> 00:46:00.503
Gradually I have seen our collectivity is learning all this.

00:46:01.159 --> 00:46:03.159
Gradually I find all those

00:46:03.471 --> 00:46:07.594
horrible dominating people have run away from Sahaja Yoga.

00:46:08.094 --> 00:46:13.913
Also I find that people are extremely loving

00:46:15.570 --> 00:46:19.982
and kindly to each other and also to others

00:46:22.703 --> 00:46:27.998
because you are embodiment of goodness, embodiment of righteousness,

00:46:28.498 --> 00:46:33.557
you are embodiment of patience, compassion, love and concern.

00:46:39.030 --> 00:46:41.030
So it is not how you can do it,

00:46:42.562 --> 00:46:44.562
you are already.

00:46:46.814 --> 00:46:49.453
But you shouldn't just give up.

00:46:49.578 --> 00:46:53.417
I said just look at something and watch.

00:46:54.324 --> 00:46:56.324
Nobody can do that, but you all can do it.

00:46:59.107 --> 00:47:02.945
So the self-esteem and then assumption.

00:47:03.445 --> 00:47:05.445
Assume your powers.

00:47:08.604 --> 00:47:12.065
If you are a guru then assume your power.

00:47:13.941 --> 00:47:15.941
You do not assume you power.

00:47:17.504 --> 00:47:19.504
You still think,

00:47:21.286 --> 00:47:25.700
God knows if I have the powers or not, this, that.

00:47:25.918 --> 00:47:27.918
That means you are just the beginners.

00:47:29.419 --> 00:47:31.419
"No, I am the guru, all right."

00:47:35.610 --> 00:47:38.868
We do say Mother I am my own guru, that's all.

00:47:39.587 --> 00:47:41.587
But is just saying from the lips.

00:47:42.400 --> 00:47:45.813
Not only that you are your own guru but of the whole world.

00:47:49.222 --> 00:47:55.014
It's a collectum Gurudom we have, I should say, collective.

00:47:56.140 --> 00:47:59.855
And nothing can escape us now. We are formidable,

00:48:00.105 --> 00:48:04.225
absolutely formidable. Nothing can escape us.

00:48:07.540 --> 00:48:10.839
If this is understood

00:48:13.622 --> 00:48:16.674
that we have to assume.

00:48:18.644 --> 00:48:23.430
Here now, elect somebody who is a very cruel man,

00:48:23.711 --> 00:48:29.407
put some clothes on him and say he's the pope, all right he's the pope.

00:48:30.595 --> 00:48:32.595
But he's not,

00:48:34.096 --> 00:48:36.096
he's just acting

00:48:36.940 --> 00:48:38.940
but inside he's not.

00:48:39.221 --> 00:48:43.691
That he's infallible! He's fallible, 100 times.

00:48:46.756 --> 00:48:48.756
That is not with us.

00:48:49.631 --> 00:48:52.590
We have all these things within ourselves.

00:48:53.090 --> 00:48:55.928
We've got them, they are there,

00:48:55.990 --> 00:48:59.329
we are the possessors of that, only thing you assume.

00:49:00.173 --> 00:49:03.874
Once you start assuming all badhas will run away, everything will run away

00:49:03.967 --> 00:49:05.269
and you'll be surprised.

00:49:05.456 --> 00:49:07.456
Who can stand a person

00:49:08.582 --> 00:49:10.582
who's a saint, who is a guru

00:49:10.675 --> 00:49:14.339
and who knows he's a guru. Nobody can stand. They'll run away.

00:49:18.624 --> 00:49:22.672
But you have to have

00:49:22.922 --> 00:49:26.726
introspection to see that your self-esteem

00:49:26.819 --> 00:49:28.819
is completely

00:49:31.509 --> 00:49:34.568
correct. It's not just you are thinking you are a Guru.

00:49:37.508 --> 00:49:39.508
I have known some real gurus

00:49:40.946 --> 00:49:42.946
and I would never allow you to go to them.

00:49:43.884 --> 00:49:48.189
God knows if you can come back in one piece or not.

00:49:50.910 --> 00:49:55.561
And I have told them, that they are real gurus, I know, but don't go near them.

00:49:58.251 --> 00:50:02.781
Because what they lack is this compassion, this Sahaj style.

00:50:03.781 --> 00:50:08.590
Because they think they have worked very hard so why should these people not work very hard.

00:50:12.969 --> 00:50:19.134
You may be anything. You can be doing this work, that work.

00:50:19.728 --> 00:50:23.466
You may be educated, not educated. Makes no difference.

00:50:23.966 --> 00:50:27.795
Whether you are rich, poor, makes no difference at all,

00:50:31.673 --> 00:50:37.191
as long as you know that you are the guru and you assume your power.

00:50:38.129 --> 00:50:40.129
In that assumption

00:50:41.317 --> 00:50:44.788
as if any talent, if you know music, you know you know music.

00:50:46.696 --> 00:50:49.197
If you know how to cook, you know how to cook,

00:50:51.261 --> 00:50:54.960
if you are an administrator and if you know administration, you know administration.

00:50:55.460 --> 00:50:59.860
But that could be also not totally absolute,

00:51:00.704 --> 00:51:03.490
but you are already absolute.

00:51:03.990 --> 00:51:06.777
Totality of reality,

00:51:07.527 --> 00:51:10.630
the reality is at your disposal.

00:51:11.130 --> 00:51:15.057
But you assume it, you are not ordinary at all.

00:51:16.526 --> 00:51:19.516
You can say you are extraordinary in ordinary.

00:51:24.583 --> 00:51:31.537
In that, you will just drop out all that is nonsensical, just drop out.

00:51:34.571 --> 00:51:36.571
Others will see you and be surprised,

00:51:38.729 --> 00:51:40.729
what sort of people these are,

00:51:42.637 --> 00:51:46.072
what sort of a life they lead, how nice they are,

00:51:46.728 --> 00:51:48.728
how kind they are.

00:51:49.791 --> 00:51:53.942
And the knowledge is so subtle and so great and

00:51:55.005 --> 00:51:57.743
of such a highest degree.

00:51:58.806 --> 00:52:01.125
But you never feel bloated up with ego.

00:52:01.218 --> 00:52:02.804
I have not seen any Sahaja yogi

00:52:02.929 --> 00:52:06.924
who says, "Oh, I know all about chakras and this and that. How dare you say like that."

00:52:07.424 --> 00:52:09.424
With the moustaches upward.

00:52:13.771 --> 00:52:18.532
No, with all this knowledge you bend down

00:52:18.657 --> 00:52:22.118
like the tree, which is laden with fruits bends down.

00:52:23.775 --> 00:52:26.156
And that humility,

00:52:26.656 --> 00:52:30.470
that simplicity and that humility gives you

00:52:32.096 --> 00:52:34.096
the special edge

00:52:36.441 --> 00:52:39.450
which can pierce into any heart.

00:52:42.984 --> 00:52:47.515
Thus you became apostles of truth.

00:52:48.422 --> 00:52:53.182
You can become prophets like William Blake, you can.

00:52:56.309 --> 00:53:00.941
So many things you'll be manifesting and you won't believe yourself.

00:53:08.354 --> 00:53:09.655
But believe,

00:53:11.844 --> 00:53:19.941
you are one with that great power which is God Almighty.

00:53:21.316 --> 00:53:24.206
They were discussing for ages I think

00:53:24.362 --> 00:53:29.708
about the immaculate conception of Christ.

00:53:30.427 --> 00:53:33.553
Such stupid people I have never seen.

00:53:35.148 --> 00:53:37.148
But he's God!

00:53:38.962 --> 00:53:42.054
He is God Almighty he is not a human being.

00:53:42.804 --> 00:53:44.804
He can do anything.

00:53:51.247 --> 00:53:53.247
How can you judge Him

00:53:53.747 --> 00:53:55.747
and judge His powers

00:53:56.716 --> 00:53:58.716
and His working, how can you.

00:54:00.311 --> 00:54:03.803
To discuss about God, have you got His brains.

00:54:06.148 --> 00:54:10.777
But it's something, a person like me discussing about banking.

00:54:15.844 --> 00:54:20.796
After say one or two sentences I go off.

00:54:23.517 --> 00:54:25.517
In the same way

00:54:26.017 --> 00:54:31.066
when you start discussing God you must know you do not have

00:54:31.973 --> 00:54:33.973
that capacity

00:54:35.005 --> 00:54:38.992
to discuss about God, what His relations are,

00:54:39.210 --> 00:54:42.114
how He got a son, this and that.

00:54:42.614 --> 00:54:43.802
Who are you!

00:54:44.709 --> 00:54:50.365
What's your own position that you can discuss?

00:54:55.056 --> 00:54:59.076
And then in that humility you realise is God Almighty,

00:55:01.317 --> 00:55:02.702
he is Almighty.

00:55:06.486 --> 00:55:12.858
He can do anything than that faith,

00:55:14.766 --> 00:55:15.665
not blind,

00:55:17.322 --> 00:55:23.170
but a real faith in that feeling that God is Almighty

00:55:25.234 --> 00:55:28.721
and that now you have become the messenger of that.

00:55:29.033 --> 00:55:33.104
God Almighty gives you all the strength, all the courage,

00:55:38.421 --> 00:55:44.979
everything, and His compassion, His love, His attention and His understanding.

00:55:45.479 --> 00:55:52.197
So this faith should be absolutely one with Him.

00:55:54.480 --> 00:55:56.669
Once I went to meet one real guru.

00:55:57.169 --> 00:55:59.169
Oh he was a very horrid fellow otherwise.

00:55:59.951 --> 00:56:04.638
He has slapped so many people, thrown so many people down from the hills

00:56:04.700 --> 00:56:10.175
and all that kinds of things he has done, no doubt. But still for me he has tremendous regards.

00:56:10.675 --> 00:56:12.675
I went to him,

00:56:14.082 --> 00:56:17.499
so he just started talking to me as if you talk to a Goddess.

00:56:19.219 --> 00:56:21.845
He said: "How do you find these worldly people here."

00:56:22.001 --> 00:56:24.849
I said: "All right, after all I have created them."

00:56:32.074 --> 00:56:34.074
Ah but he said "Still but,

00:56:34.574 --> 00:56:38.601
you are God with your power why don't you change them a little bit.".

00:56:40.884 --> 00:56:44.942
I said: "That's what is problem. I have given them freedom.

00:56:45.442 --> 00:56:49.207
I have said all right it's freedom to you.

00:56:50.645 --> 00:56:55.891
You can choose if you want to get transformed or not, I cannot force you."

00:56:57.329 --> 00:57:00.840
He said: "But God Almighty you are, you can do anything."

00:57:02.935 --> 00:57:07.311
I said: "I can do everything but I do not want to do certain things.

00:57:08.468 --> 00:57:14.904
One of them is to take away the freedom from them.

00:57:15.404 --> 00:57:17.404
That is their freedom to choose

00:57:18.248 --> 00:57:21.771
that's given to them because if they are to have the ultimate freedom

00:57:21.830 --> 00:57:24.271
they should have this little freedom intact."

00:57:27.930 --> 00:57:29.930
So he was quarrelling with me about this,

00:57:30.774 --> 00:57:32.774
he said "But when you are God Almighty

00:57:33.774 --> 00:57:35.774
there could be some other method

00:57:36.026 --> 00:57:38.821
these horrible people, what to do?" 

00:57:41.198 --> 00:57:43.198
I said: "Your concern is all right.

00:57:44.761 --> 00:57:47.866
I understand because you are a guru,

00:57:49.492 --> 00:57:52.523
but when I am God Almighty supposing,

00:57:53.742 --> 00:57:58.101
then, my style is different. I can't be like you."

00:57:59.696 --> 00:58:04.051
Then he said "That's true, you can't be like me."

00:58:07.009 --> 00:58:10.101
That is what I have found in him.

00:58:10.135 --> 00:58:12.220
He was talking to me only

00:58:12.466 --> 00:58:15.514
as if I am God standing before him.

00:58:20.276 --> 00:58:23.597
And then he told all the disciples, "You see, you praise,

00:58:24.203 --> 00:58:26.203
you praise the Lord, praise Her.

00:58:26.880 --> 00:58:29.693
Suti kara, because

00:58:29.998 --> 00:58:31.596
God is fond of praise."

00:58:34.166 --> 00:58:36.166
I said "Really." "Yes.

00:58:38.418 --> 00:58:39.783
If you praise the Lord

00:58:39.876 --> 00:58:41.876
then he gives you everything. I have seen that.

00:58:42.057 --> 00:58:43.306
I always praise Him.

00:58:44.443 --> 00:58:46.443
Whenever I want something to be done

00:58:46.554 --> 00:58:48.554
I just praise Him and He does it for me."

00:58:51.779 --> 00:58:53.923
So, I said "it's true,

00:58:54.883 --> 00:58:58.097
I must accept it." It's Bhakti Gamya.

00:59:00.013 --> 00:59:03.306
You cannot get to Mother

00:59:03.381 --> 00:59:05.936
unless and until you have really bhakti from your heart.

00:59:05.993 --> 00:59:11.951
Is all already sort of a built in restriction,

00:59:12.009 --> 00:59:13.120
what can you do.

00:59:14.204 --> 00:59:17.374
If you don't have bhakti you cannot get to Mother,

00:59:17.874 --> 00:59:18.931
no you cannot.

00:59:19.431 --> 00:59:20.592
You cannot get to God.

00:59:23.021 --> 00:59:27.446
But if you have bhakti then you can get to Mother.

00:59:27.946 --> 00:59:29.946
Is written Bhakti Gamya.

00:59:32.269 --> 00:59:34.502
If somebody says "All right. Raise my Kundalini."

00:59:36.064 --> 00:59:41.629
I cannot raise his Kundalini, not, but for seven lives he won't have realisation.

00:59:42.819 --> 00:59:47.204
But if somebody says "Mother will you please give me realisation." at once.

00:59:49.756 --> 00:59:51.920
So not only humility but bhakti.

00:59:52.969 --> 00:59:55.952
And bhakti is only possible if you have your faith.

00:59:56.452 --> 00:59:58.452
That's the thing is the faith

00:59:58.952 --> 01:00:03.165
which is challenged nowadays by all kinds of stupid people; intellectuals,

01:00:03.205 --> 01:00:05.205
these horrible people who are

01:00:05.369 --> 01:00:07.138
taking out the /?/ out of their heads, 

01:00:07.160 --> 01:00:09.789
or also by science and this so called

01:00:09.882 --> 01:00:12.391
catholic church and this church and that church.

01:00:17.191 --> 01:00:21.658
So your faith in God has to be absolutely,

01:00:21.857 --> 01:00:27.608
absolutely untarnishable.

01:00:28.108 --> 01:00:33.255
Nothing can disturb that. That's very important.

01:00:34.570 --> 01:00:37.062
You have seen all the miracles of God.

01:00:37.195 --> 01:00:42.107
You have seen how you working out His powers.

01:00:43.952 --> 01:00:50.645
You have known all these things. But still the faith in God is missing.

01:00:52.004 --> 01:00:58.370
But the person who has complete faith on God is called as the one ... is God himself they say.

01:01:00.663 --> 01:01:02.663
Is called as Paramachaitanya.

01:01:05.486 --> 01:01:07.486
The Guru is called as

01:01:08.760 --> 01:01:14.010
the one who is himself Brahmachaitanya.

01:01:17.810 --> 01:01:22.386
So when this faith in God

01:01:22.886 --> 01:01:25.859
is absolutely established in you,

01:01:26.929 --> 01:01:32.527
that there is God Almighty, he's Almighty,

01:01:33.027 --> 01:01:37.645
and that I am the messenger of that God.

01:01:39.001 --> 01:01:44.637
Just this understanding when it becomes absolutely firm in you,

01:01:45.137 --> 01:01:47.671
then you are in the Guru Pada.

01:01:49.190 --> 01:01:52.967
I bless you today that all of you achieve that state

01:01:53.467 --> 01:01:58.028
that you reside in that Guru Pada state.

01:01:58.528 --> 01:02:00.409
And where, wherever you are,

01:02:00.909 --> 01:02:05.275
whatever may be your position, whatever you may do,

01:02:09.524 --> 01:02:11.524
the faith in the God Almighty

01:02:12.757 --> 01:02:15.819
that is so truly within you will express itself.

01:02:16.849 --> 01:02:18.849
Not only but that it will manifest.

01:02:20.123 --> 01:02:23.310
It will act, just like God.

01:02:29.229 --> 01:02:31.229
So many things can be said.

01:02:31.485 --> 01:02:33.485
I have said so many things before.

01:02:34.433 --> 01:02:37.501
And so many can be said later on also

01:02:39.020 --> 01:02:41.463
but today we have to remember one thing

01:02:41.596 --> 01:02:45.619
that we must have complete faith

01:02:45.915 --> 01:02:47.711
in the Kingdom of God

01:02:47.804 --> 01:02:52.409
and in the powers of God Almighty, complete faith,

01:02:53.805 --> 01:02:55.805
and then in ourselves.

01:02:57.609 --> 01:02:59.609
May God bless you all.
